title: Converse Jack Purcell x Hancock Vulcanised Articles
description:
Converse and Hancock Vulcanised Articles partner for a weatherized take on the Converse Jack Purcell sneaker.

The British clothiers bring their expertise in hand-crafted outerwear to the Jack Purcell Mid, outfitting it in water resistant materials and unique design details.

Music:

"Step Into My Office" by Blank Paper
